Fabian T. Garcia

Age : 57Public asset : 5,694,920 USDLinked companies :  Kimberly Clark Corp -  Revlon Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Fabian T. Garcia is Chief Operating Officer-Global Innovation & Growth at Hill's Pet Nutrition, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at Revlon Consumer Products Corp., Revlon, Inc. and Kimberly-Clark Corp. Mr. Garcia was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Elizabeth Arden, Inc., COO-Global Innovation & Growth by Colgate-Palmolive Co., a Principal by Procter & Gamble Co., and Senior Vice President-International by Timberland LLC.He also served on the board at Decorize, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Boliver Simon.



