Fabian T. Garcia 

		
		CEO, 

	
		 Revlon Inc. 	

 
Last Updated: 03/18/2017 



Executive Summary
Fabian Garcia is the President and Chief Executive Officer of Revlon, the New York City-based cosmetics, skin care, fragrance, and personal care company founded in 1932. He came to Revlon in April 2016 from consumer products giant the Colgate-Palmolive Company, where he most recently served as Chief Operating Officer of Global Innovati 
Personal Attributes and Interests

Garcia is married and has four children.
Garcia replaced Lorenzo Delpani, who stepped down as CEO of Revlon on March 1, 2016, citing personal reasons. Delpani remains a member of the Revlon board. “Revlon is a true global 
Current Focus

Company Snapshot: Revlon Inc. is a global cosmetics, hair color, hair care and hair treatments, beauty tools, men’s grooming products, anti-perspirant deodorants, fragrances, skincare, and other beauty care produc 
Key Challenges

