Biographical Highlights

Born circa 1960.
Garcia earned a Bachelor of Science degree in Chemical Engineering from Simon Bolivar University in Caracas, Venezuela. 
Other Boards and Organizations

Former Member, Board of Directors, GuildMaster Inc.
Former Member, Board of Directors, Colgate-Palmolive Ltd., Pakistan 
 





